FIGHTER BOMBER
        Choose the F-15 or the Phantom F-3a because they carry more
bombs and mavericks. Always arm your plane with sidewinders, in case
of enemy planes. Choose the F-15 Tomcat as your enemy as this plane is
the easiest to kill. If you get enemy aircraft arround you, fly
slowly, and don't move around much. Fire lots of flares, and when the
enemy is behind you, fly right around.
        Always use sidewinders, but use the gun to conserve missiles.
When you get to the mission "BRIDGE END", use afterburners. When you
get top speed, switch off your engine. Slow down to 250Km and put your
afterburners on. Keep doing this until you near the target. When the
SAM sight fires, use your afterburners, fire four Mavericks and keep
using the flares until it's destroyed. You must fly very low th hit
the bridge.
        Type BUCKAROO as the pilots name, and you can choose one of
the 16 missions.


EYE OF HORUS
        Type SPAM in the credits section for infinate lives, and you
don't need the correct colour coded keys anymore. Set is located
through the blue locked loft.


CRACKDOWN
        type SMURF and then press F1 and F2 to give unlimited lives to
your two characters.


STRIDER
        Play the game, and press F9 to pause, now hold down <help>,
<left shift>, and "1", release the keys, and unpause the game with
F10.
        Pressing keys 1 - 5, you can skip through the levels
respectivly. Pressing F1 - F4 gives you differant points in the level.


