BEVERLY HILLS COP
        To play any level, click past the high-score table, onto the
screen where you select the difficulty factor and type MELLIE, all
levels will be avaliable.


VIGILANTE
        Enter your name as POOKY IS MY PAL in the highscore table, and
now F1 increases your lives, and F8 goes to the next level.


IVANHOE
        Pause the game, and type JC IS THE BEST and press <RETURN>.
Press "N" to advance a level, <delete> to kill all bad guys on screen.
On the intermediary bonus screens, press <ctrl> to wipe out the
heavyweight.


PUFFYS SAGA
        Press F5 and F6 together during the game and be transported to
level seven.


DYNASTY WARS
        When the title screen apperas type CHEAT MODE. Press F2 to
advance a level.


E-MOTION
        Type in the name from the title screen when the game loads. F1
then advances through the levels, "F" moves you forward ten levels.
Use F3 and F4 to move beckwards.


